            <title>[DATAREST-62] NullPointerException in RepositoryEntityController</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/DATAREST-62</link>
                <project id="10901" key="DATAREST">Spring Data REST</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. &lt;tt&gt;git clone &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/olivergierke/spring-restbucks.git&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/olivergierke/spring-restbucks.git&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
