                            <comment id="87234" author="olivergierke" created="Wed, 23 Jan 2013 06:13:25 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After some further playing with it, this is probably related to the fact that &lt;tt&gt;@RestResource(exported = false&lt;/tt&gt; is not considered during the rendering of the home controller. The &lt;tt&gt;PaymentRepository&lt;/tt&gt; is in fact annotated with that annotation, so it shouldn&apos;t be exposed in the first place. Still, accessing a URL for a non-exposed repository shouldn&apos;t lead to a &lt;tt&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/tt&gt; but a &lt;tt&gt;404 Not Found&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="88526" author="jbrisbin" created="Wed, 6 Mar 2013 12:19:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Testing with the latest snapshots, this gives a 404 now instead of an error.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
